man3-375x195.png)](http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=5EjG-1U3wqA#!)

Screen capture of “the Mandarin” from Iron Man 3's trailer.

  
The Walt Disney Company China, Marvel Studios and DMG Entertainment
[announced](http://marvel.com/news/story/18550/iron_man_3_to_be_co-
produced_in_china) back in April that they were intended to co-produce “Iron
Man 3″ in China. Stan from China Hearsay
[doubts](http://www.chinahearsay.com/iron-man-3-and-sino-foreign-film-co-
productions-an-update) if the mainland Chinese censor would accept the villain
of the
[movie](http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=5EjG-1U3wqA#!)
being “The Mandarin”.

